sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Pulls inbox items from Workday for specified date range.

Inputs :

  • Start Date Time - Start Date from which you want to pull the workday inbox items.
  • Report Owner Username - Username of the user who created custom RAAS report in Workday.
  • Report Name - Custom RAAS report name.
  • End Date Time - End Date to which you want to pull the workday inbox items. If not provided then current date will be considered.
  • Data Source Reference - Data Source where you want to attach the incoming inbox items report.

Outputs :

  • Status - If the request is executed successfully, Status is set to "Success". If there is a failure in Workday, Status is set to "Error".
  • Error Message - Reason for error. Populated only when an error occurs.

Error Messages :

  • Unable to Authenticate access token. Please check credential details in Connection and Credential Aliases of Workday HR Spoke.
  • Encountered an error. Check log for more details.

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
